<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.6">
<l>eṉtuṇai yeṉṟeṭuttēṟ kiṟaiyēṉumi raṅkiṟṟilaḷ</l>
<l>taṉtuṇai yāyaveṉṟaṉ taṉimaikkumi raṅkiṟṟilaḷ</l>
<l>vaṉtuṇai vāṉavarkkāy varañceṟṟaraṅ kattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>iṉtuṇai vaṉoṭumpō yeḻilālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She is without even a bit of pity for me who raised her as my companion;</l>
<l>She is without pity even for my loneliness, [me] who was her companion</l>
<l>Are they setting out for elegant Āli, [as she] goes with the one</l>
<l rend="indent">who is [her] sweet companion</l>
<l>Who dwells in Araṅkam, destroying the boons [of demons],</l>
<l rend="indent">as the constant companion of the celestials?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
